sequenceDiagram
    actor Robot as 机器人/操作员
    participant API as API Gateway<br/>(Golang)
    participant UploadSvc as Upload Service<br/>(Golang)
    participant ObjStore as 对象存储<br/>(MinIO/S3)
    participant Pipeline as 处理流水线<br/>(Python Worker)
    participant MetaDB as 元数据 DB<br/>(PostgreSQL)

    Robot->>API: POST /episodes/upload/init<br/>{filename, size, format, checksum}
    API->>MetaDB: 创建 Episode (status=UPLOADING)<br/>创建 UploadSession
    API-->>Robot: {episode_id, session_id, chunk_size}

    loop 每个分块 (1-10GB 文件 / ~64MB chunk)
        Robot->>API: PUT /episodes/upload/{session_id}/chunk/{n}<br/>{chunk_data}
        API->>UploadSvc: 转发分块
        UploadSvc->>ObjStore: 写入临时分块
        UploadSvc->>MetaDB: 更新 received_chunks
        API-->>Robot: 200 OK {received: n}
    end

    Robot->>API: POST /episodes/upload/{session_id}/complete
    API->>UploadSvc: 触发组装
    UploadSvc->>ObjStore: 合并分块 → 正式文件路径
    UploadSvc->>MetaDB: UploadSession status=COMPLETED<br/>Episode status=PROCESSING
    UploadSvc->>Pipeline: 发布消息 EpisodeIngested {episode_id}
    API-->>Robot: 202 Accepted {episode_id, status: "processing"}

    Pipeline->>ObjStore: 读取 MCAP/HDF5 文件
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: 校验 MD5 / 解析格式<br/>提取 Topics + 时间范围<br/>生成预览帧<br/>计算质量评分
    Pipeline->>MetaDB: 写入 Topic 记录<br/>更新 Episode metadata<br/>Episode status=READY
    Pipeline-->>API: 事件 EpisodeReady {episode_id}

    Note over Robot,MetaDB: 断点续传: Robot 可携带 session_id 续传未完成分块
